title: Hotel Relais Saint-Honoré
description:
The Relais Saint-Honoré is one of those charming little hotels where you immediately feel at home. The old furniture and exposed beams contribute to the rustic and welcoming charm of the hotel. Comfort is the watchword in this friendly hotel where the rooms are warm and intimate.
More than just a sophisticated design, the Relais Saint-Honoré enjoys a great locations. The area is perfect to simply wander around town, go window-shopping in the luxurious shops of the street, not to mention the famous Colette concept-store. Definitely worth seeing!
Just a few steps away from the hotel, the Place du marché Saint-Honoré is a lovely paved square surrounded by numerous restaurants, each one more appetizing than the next. In addition, the hotel is located near the most symbolic places in Paris: the Opera, the Louvre, place Vendôme, the Tuileries garden... Nature, culture and delicacy, all the conditions promising of an unforgettable stay.
